data.description: Move-in ready, no waiting to build. Fantastic 1-story Eclipse model with 3-car split garage in Lennar's newer exclusive 55+ gated Heritage Solaire. Many extras and upgrades + amazing Wine Room! Desirable location within friendly, active community, where residents have access to wide selection of amenities. Spacious Great Room//Dining Room flows to gourmet kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, two ovens, microwave, gorgeous Quartz counters, big island with extra seating, pretty cabinets with roll-out drawers. Large inside Laundry Room has sink + plenty of storage. Solar, shutters, updated lighting, Ring Doorbell, tankless water heater. Fully landscaped front and back yard with no rear neighbors, water feature, covered patio, automatic sun screen, lots of beautiful plantings. Community garden, amphitheater, Clubhouse pool/spa, pickleball, tennis, Bocce, BBQ. Inside Sol Centre are TV and activity rooms, fitness center, kitchen, wine bar. Accessible to Lake Tahoe, Napa, Bay Area, recreational pursuits, lots of golf courses. Near many Roseville conveniences, restaurants, medical, shopping. HOA maintains front yards. Solar community has reliable Roseville Electric Utilities. Smart home is state-of-the-art integrating high-tech elements for optimal security and quality of life.
